Rory McIlroy played in the traditional Par-3 Contest at Augusta National on Wednesday . 
  One Direction singer Niall Horan caddied for the Northern Irishman in the contest . 
  Tiger Woods also played the contest for the first time in 11 years . 
  Kevin Streelman won the contest after a play-off against Camilo Villegas . 
  Horan slipped while carrying McIlory's clubs on the par-three course . 
 